{
  "stem": "12564.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they came to the woods, and they offered us food, and we were sitting with them together until the news came that the Germans already bypassed us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Russians came into town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after a couple of days, we went to a city with the name Krasnik.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-R-A-S-N-I-K.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this city was a small Jewish community coming to life from all the woods, from the bunkers, the survivors that we met, everybody over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the city, we felt that it's not safe to be any longer to after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three of my wives-- she wasn't my wife at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My girlfriend's cousins went back to town where my [? wife ?] was hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way back from town to Krasnik, they all were killed, after the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The polish people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chaszow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "C-H-A-S-Z-O-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is seven kilometers from the town where I was hiding, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over, and we were still hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were still afraid to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another friend went by train to Krakow, which was liberated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a pogrom in a city by the name Kielce in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was killed by stoning her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were afraid to move by train, even after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Kielce pogrom is very well known.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was written up all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know this-- she was hiding with us in the woods, this person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Got killed after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that is the same people what they killed so much of us before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did not change.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day when the Russian came in, they want to kill us much more not to leave witnesses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the name of the game.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not this one, I have other one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told myself never to be without.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
